This paper deals with the extension of Answer Set Programming (ASP) with epistemic operators, which is a topic that falls under the category of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the translation of Epistemic Logic Programs (ELPs) into non-ground ASP, which is related to Logic in Computer Science (cs.LO) and Programming Languages (cs.PL). The implementation of the encoding method into the prototype ELP solving system also involves Computational Linguistics (cs.CL) and Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DL).
